    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014basically showroom quality! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. I'm really sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
