      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced double-VANOS system, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers. Rod bearing replacement has been performed as preventative maintenance, and the factory Carbon Black finish remains in concours-ready condition. A mechanically pristine, driver-focused masterpiece.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
