      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since the day it was driven off the lot. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero imperfections, while the interior remains pristine, retaining that signature 'new car' scent and supple leather upholstery. Meticulously garage-kept and serviced exclusively at the dealership, it performs flawlessly with whisper-quiet operation and precise handling. Every button, dial, and feature functions as if it were day one. For the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise, this is the finest example available on the market today.",
      "price": 48500.0,
